com.revature.Services

Interface ViewAudiCars

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ViewAudi

    public interface ViewAudiCars
    An Audi car viewing service.

    This interface provides a method that allows the user to either view all the cars on the lot if they are a customer, or allows the user to view all the cars in the AWS RDS database if they are an employee.

    Author:
    josecanela

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void viewAudis(java.lang.String username, java.lang.String password)
